<section xml:id="sec-simplexmax" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>The Simplex Algorithm for Canonical Maximization</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      Having established the pivot in <xref ref="sec-pivot"/>, we use geometry to determine where to pivot to find optimal solutions.
      We also discuss how to address potential obstacles.
    </p>
  </introduction>

